"※ The chainage length specifies the number of nodes along the curve. A "
"shorter chainage length results in more nodes. "
msgstr "※　使用桩距控制曲线上的节点密度。桩距越短节点越密。"

#: ../src\yakxin\columbina\features\fillet\FilletDialog.java:79
